c2f7e06a296b7","tid":138092,"uid":25748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"我架車換左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換左一年行左一萬公里未覺避震有柴"},{"pid":"a32719bd9761bb2152edfdab1ccef59b7cf9724d","tid":138092,"uid":25748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會坐得好唔舒服<br />\nfull load嘅話，個碌可能會high到個殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇彈弓磅數<br />\n有啲low低彈弓只係比原廠low低&lt;30mm<br />\n磅數硬返啲啲compensate返，唔會話好唔舒服同撞沙板"},{"pid":"958ac79508196793a9865cac42db3f26cfe972b7","tid":138092,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"1.會打柴<br />\n2.好跳唔舒服"},{"pid":"3300c8312e51822e024bc9f2e7ecbaed3530c88c","tid":138092,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"買彈弓加裝工不如加多兩三千買套避震"},{"pid":"613ff01063c8b1df5dbe4b49aee2c7af2255406a","tid":138092,"uid":5464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"我唔識車 但係老豆應該較低左架車 行老龍都成日刮沙板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b0e6e7e23205b5c56abcdb43dde8f6cfa7b0a8","tid":138092,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"唔建議，避震機會好快收皮"},{"pid":"fd28b21b912a692755df08482fbd9067c65acf6d","tid":138092,"uid":41632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"唔計支原裝避震機會快啲打柴<br />\n冇咁舒服 灣冇咁定 冇咁伏<br />\n最後都係換返全太絞牙<br />\n唔好晒錢啦"},{"pid":"82184174a887c6cfc76244487449fc22f93faa56","tid":138092,"uid":41632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔計支原裝避震機會快啲打柴<br />\n冇咁舒服 灣冇咁定 冇咁伏<br />\n最後都係換返全<span style=\"color: red;\">套</span>絞牙<br />\n唔好晒錢啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8acf767e0318900dfae4613160cd425519169460","tid":138092,"u